380
00:21:37.636 --> 00:21:39.512 
<font color="#ffffff">Silvan Meyer.</font>

381
00:21:42.809 --> 00:21:44.937 
<font color="#ffffff">Schutzkleidung, Waffen, Deckung:</font>

382
00:21:45.260 --> 00:21:47.129 
<font color="#ffffff">Was am Trainingstag des Paintball</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Verband Swiss</font>

383
00:21:47.452 --> 00:21:49.872 
